title: dashboard/app: builder daemon mails contain broken link
body:
Example: https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/golang-dev/dT04n6MVduU

The link on the 
```Reviewed-on: ```
line goes to https://go-review.googlesource.com/1630Reviewed-by, the correct one is https://go-review.googlesource.com/1630
